          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "<i>Data Visualization Reporter Sita Vemuri can be contacted at </i><a href=\"mailto:sita.vemuri@columbiaspectator.com\"><i>sita.vemuri@columbiaspectator.com</i></a><i>.</i><a href=\"mailto:eliza.lamster@columbiaspectator.com\"><i> </i></a>"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "<b><i>Want to keep up with breaking news? Subscribe to our </i></b><a href=\"https://columbiaspectator.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe?u=a3d2eeb1ae5560ca04f82f042&id=e51c51d62d\"><b><i>email newsletter</i></b></a><b><i> and like Spectator on </i></b><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/columbiaspectator\"><b><i>Facebook</i></b></a><b><i>. </i></b>"
          }
        ],
        "headline": "Spreak-ing news: Scenes from Spectator photographers’ Spring break",
        "dek": "From coast to coast and valley to valley, over spring break, Spectator’s photographers adjusted their lenses to subjects: familiar and new. Take a closer look at what our staff photographers did on their days off.",
        "date": "April 3rd, 2026",
        "byline": "By <a href=\"https://www.columbiaspectator.com/contributors/audrea-chen/\">Audrea Chen</a>, <a href=\"https://www.columbiaspectator.com/contributors/tori-fergus/\">Tori Fergus</a>, <a href=\"https://www.columbiaspectator.com/contributors/esmeralda-paredes/\">Esmeralda Paredes</a>, <a href=\"https://www.columbiaspectator.com/contributors/tianqi-wang/\">Tianqi Wang</a>, <a href=\"https://www.columbiaspectator.com/contributors/salem-maru/\">Salem Maru</a>, <a href=\"https://www.columbiaspectator.com/contributors/sofia-wadler/\">Sofia Wadler</a>, <a href=\"https://www.columbiaspectator.com/contributors/jackson-dilks/\">Jackson Dilks</a>,  <a href=\"https://www.columbiaspectator.com/contributors/marcus-bui/\">Marcus Bui</a>, <a href=\"https://www.columbiaspectator.com/contributors/max-yoo/\">Max Yoo</a>, <a href=\"https://www.columbiaspectator.com/contributors/ming-yuan/\">Ming Yuan</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.columbiaspectator.com/contributors/logan-fencer/\">Logan Fencer</a>",
        "byline2": "Web Design by <a href=\"https://www.columbiaspectator.com/contributors/sita-vemuri/\">Sita Vemuri</a>",
        "cover_asset": "/images/3-Salem_Maru_Spreak_DPE-4.jpg",
        "cover_caption": "A morning captured beside a dock, soaking in Guatemalan sun Salem Maru / Deputy Photo Editor",
